Package: introstats
Type: Package
Title: R as an Interactive Educational Environment for Introductory Statistics
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-02-21
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Walter", email = "dswalter@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows students with a limited programming
    background to use R as an interactive educational environment 
    for basic statistics. In particular, installation of this package 
    provides access to scripts that leverage R to interactively introduce
    content ranging from p-values to confidence intervals to stability in 
    time series.
License: GPL
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    shiny
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0),
    Rcmdr,
    RcmdrPlugin.epack,
    ggplot2
